        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks WB for his note, states that it will be taken care of on the publication of CD’s book [<hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Mentions loss of many months owing to illness.</p>
            <p>Thanks WB for favour to CD’s son.</p>
